Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:13.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already late November.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.07,0:01:20.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one month left of this busy, dizzy second semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:40.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:43.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:44.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:50.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the friendliest morning greeting I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:54.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it every day if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:55.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:57.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:00.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan, you seem happy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:03.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:05.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it's cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:08.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost New Year's, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:11.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:15.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still November.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:18.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:19.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:23.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:24.83,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's wearing a blazer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:29.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So fresh. Ever since spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:34.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice my bedhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:40.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:47.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I should have just pretended that's how I wanted it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:53.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, you gotta see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.05,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Bedhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:07.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're selling Ogura flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.39,0:03:09.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a juice box sampling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it when he's with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:12.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like he's having so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I used to think,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.67,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“Wow, everyone's gathering around him.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:27.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“I wish I could be like Kazehaya-kun.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all red.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Time flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:40.46,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think my feelings are moving forward as well, step by step.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, he's getting annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That college student?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:02.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Day in, day out, all day, every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“What are you doing?”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:04.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Who are you with?”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Let's meet up.”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Why don't you answer right away?”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Why can't you come out?”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Are you with a guy?”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:17.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wake up, come to school and attend class with my classmates, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at night, I sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:21.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:25.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going out with a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He picked me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:36.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always get picked up by the kind of guy who acts like a big grown-up only at first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:42.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to think hanging out with girls was a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I think guys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:47.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it normally is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:50.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think there's a serious mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:55.69,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be crazy about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:01.43,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess everyone's relationship is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:02.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:05.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming over tonight, be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me play the rest of that game from last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:12.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you want to play against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:18.88,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan and Sanada-kun sort of have the same air about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:22.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all about Chizuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.10,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:28.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't too many couples this perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Chizu-chan thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:39.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she like Sanada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey old man, busy day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:45.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I'll help with the store during the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're our poster girl after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But damn man,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You getting ready to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:17.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:20.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:25.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, I died!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean chimera.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:35.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered you talking in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't talk in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:43.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That lion... that lion... chimera...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:53.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New mitts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under 500 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything other than a shoulder massage coupon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:07.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything's fine. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I'm giving you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, on New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:29.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:30.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:39.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:47.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:52.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Dad's taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, Yano-chin, come shopping with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:18.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:20.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:24.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seeing my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:26.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see him as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:28.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you buying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu's birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:54.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how I'm kinda loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:01.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always giving me the look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:06.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know her name, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:11.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe in destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:16.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear our destiny stepping towards us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:19.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:20.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:23.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you give him last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have money, so I gave him a shoulder massage coupon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoulder massage coupon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:40.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used it all up right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours of shoulder massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She cares for him so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:49.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My budget's 500 yen this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:02.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get him new mitts, but a glove pouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:20.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm gonna spend some money on him this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:22.75,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an impulsive buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad for you, Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miniskirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:45.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:56.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramen, ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:57.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:07.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel like I could ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Chizu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is there someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:17.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:24.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was random.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been a crush, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Always?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:35.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had a crush for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:38.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:41.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known him since we were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:44.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:53.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only thinks of me like a little sister, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:55.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:02.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:08.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not even going to look at me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to become an awesome woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:15.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows once I'm grown up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:20.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:24.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:29.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it sort of sucks that I don't get to meet him often.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:34.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives in Sapporo. Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:39.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't come back for the Obon festival last year, so I haven't seen him in like a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:43.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just know he'll be back for New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:46.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch, I'm a high schooler now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:52.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:54.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I just ask straight out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:55.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:13:00.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sanada-kun that you like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, are you talking about Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:13.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:18.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu's important to me, like a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:21.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously wouldn't mind being his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister? Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:31.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ryu's brother that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,does Sanada-kun know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:53.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:57.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shout, Sanada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:11.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:12.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was cheering up Joe and Tanaka and the lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's so wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:28.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're getting together to cheer Joe up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free next weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:32.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:36.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't, not next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:44.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have guts to wear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan's shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:02.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:07.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be happy to meet someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:09.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:14.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:18.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:23.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kazehaya, what do you think of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:25.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, winter clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:28.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the miniskirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:35.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15,000—Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:37.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:41.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted it for New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:45.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting some for your New Year's allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:50.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Tohru's here only on New Year's Eve or New Year's Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:56.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:08.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:11.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got dumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:25.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dumped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't easy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:34.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him straight up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:50.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Ayane?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:57.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy didn't hear a thing I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:00.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't like him after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:06.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were meeting him for some quality time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:08.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After what I told you? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:12.51,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of any words of consolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:20.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that this is what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:27.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting like I just got dumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got rejected too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both heartbroken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:38.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking up is part of dating, but it still sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:43.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said {\i1}I{\i0} dumped {\i1}him{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to act tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:52.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't told her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:05.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:13.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for me to decide what to do after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:17.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that's what you'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:21.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:28.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd end up like a really bad drama if she saw my brother without knowing the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:32.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:36.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A miniskirt? For New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:37.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a frilly one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:42.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about one that'll look good on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:44.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:46.83,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:50.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what your crush is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we come too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:00.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:06.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting all hyped up while Yano-chin's upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:09.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:16.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet at my place to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:18.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:20.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sleep over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:21.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should come too, Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:25.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep over? Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all play against each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:30.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least wait 'til I say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I was changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:46.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:48.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't come too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you having any?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:00.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:14.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:16.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:21.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chizuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:22.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:23.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:53.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always busy just trying to talk to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:58.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never had time to think about relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:04.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Relationships must be just as hard as friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:15.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be because I like Kazehaya-kun, that I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:34.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crumbling smiles, never tarnished.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:38.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:40.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
